title: AWS DynamoDB: Summary
agents: aws
catalog: cloud/aws
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check gives an overall summary of the tables managed by DynamoDB.
 It reports the total number of tables, the number of tables per region
 as well as the following per-table information: name, number of items,
 size and status.

 To make this check work, you have to configure the related special
 agent {Amazon Web Services (AWS)}.

discovery:
 One service is created.
